<span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">প্রত্যাশিদের</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;"> </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">জন্য</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">- </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">ইংরেজি</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;"> - </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">স্পোকেন</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">, </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">রাইটিং</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">, </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">আইএলটিএস</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">, </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">প্রনান্সিয়েশন</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;"> </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">ও</span><span style="font-family: 'Nunito'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;"> </span><span style="font-family: 'Nirmala UI'; font-size: 10.5pt; color: #000000;">প্রেজেন্টেশন।</span><br />
